	<h4 class="c-issue-toc__article-title" id="1595"><a href="/pl/archiwum/2015/9-pomniki-transformacji/slabe-obrazy">Poor Images</a></h4>
	<h5 class="c-issue-toc__article-authors"><!--Authors:--><a href="/en/bio?id=1039">Marek Krajewski</a></h5>
	
				<a class="c-issue-toc__article-collapse-btn" role="button" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#collapseDoi1595" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseSummary1595" data-lexicon-show="show" data-lexicon-hide="hide">
